issue.body: I was editing some dates of when I had watched shows from the history tab and discovered that upon selecting a new date and time, the timestamp saved for the episode would be off by four hours. I am in the EDT Time zone which is 4 hours off of GMT so I think this might be a bug in assuming a timestamp needs to be converted from GMT to EDT when it is already in EDT. Please let me know if you need anymore information and thanks for your incredible work!
